description:
This additional content includes:

- "C Summer Snorkel" Palamute layered armor piece
- "C Summer Suit" Palamute layered armor piece

Get your Palamute ready for the seaside with this fun summer outfit!

Dress up your buddy with this special layered armor!

- Buddy layered armor can be used in the Layered Armor Settings menu of the Buddy Board.
- Layered armor is a "skin" which changes the appearance of the character without affecting their stats and abilities.
name: "C Summer" Palamute layered armor set
